Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很同情Globe那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們不知道Kivotos計畫的選拔成員
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是由你而選出的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很同情久部社長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本想像不到被我們所利用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Albion是因為迷戀avator的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不討厭就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:01:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是10年前在夏威夷島上拍攝到的西頓公司研究設施的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家公司做了巧妙的隱蔽工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實質上是Macbeth Enterprises的子公司
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得照片上的人就是前幾日侵入這裡的那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然幕後黑手是Macbeth Enterprises嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人是Designer's Child吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在神田事件期間他們都在國外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國內所保護的6人中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了嵐哲平外其他人都失去了蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哲平一樣 其它的Designer's Child
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以使用Machine Goodfellow成為KILL-T-GANG吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得既然KILL-T-GANG已經進入活動期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就意味著他們已經做好了準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們為什麼不更加頻繁地進攻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平成為KILL-T-GANG的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華好像使用了布盧姆中所積聚的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據哲平說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當於KILL-T-GANG母艦規模的飛船停泊在天王星的衛星軌道上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們因能量耗盡而無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才使用Machine Goodfellow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地球人身上獲取KILL-T-GANG活動所需的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是人類的力比多…生命力能量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這件事我還沒有彙報給總部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果SaltyDog得知Machine Goodfellow和KILL-T-GANG之間的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他們會獨斷先發制人 甚至不惜偽裝成恐怖份子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Macbeth所在的東京進行核攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.91,0:02:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使留下的人類因此而得救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令也不會接受這種做法吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此巨大的危機竟然沒有洩露到社會上 真是太不可思議了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 在古巴危機的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果蘇聯將核武帶入古巴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會引發美蘇的全面戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時媒體也炒得沸沸揚揚的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終蘇聯讓步了 危機得以被避免
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少表面上是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而實際上 蘇聯已經在古巴配備了100枚以上的核彈頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道這事的只有總統和他的幾個親密顧問而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到冷戰結束30年後 這事才被公開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種重大的危機為什麼沒有被洩露這事讓人覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許僅需5分就會造成一國滅亡的危機 告訴民眾又有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種真正的危機 通常都會被隱蔽起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這歷史上很常見…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:09.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所有的歡笑 所有的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:09.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑顔も涙もきっと全て
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:16.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一切都是為了與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:16.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君に出会うためだった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:35.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}漱漱而下的淚水 在風中飄散
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:35.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}こぼれ行く涙風が連れて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:43.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}以生疏的動作 無數次伸出手去追求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:43.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}慣れない仕草でその先へ何度も手を伸ばした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:48.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那個不善於表達而受傷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:48.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}言葉足らずで傷つけた人よ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:54.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}現在已經背負起不可磨滅的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:54.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう取り消せない過去を背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:58.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}踏出了新的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:58.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}踏み出して行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:04.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑顔も涙もきっと全て
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:04.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所有的歡笑 所有的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:11.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君に出会うための理由だった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:11.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一切都是為了與你相遇的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:17.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明日があるたったそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:17.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只因為這一個理由 就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:23.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕ら生きる意味になって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:23.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那將成為我們生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:30.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そしてまた日が照らすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:30.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}太陽將再次照耀大地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是西瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的生活不會持續太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:05:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹是這樣告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羨慕你能和皮兹交流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有女主角範范兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一台KILL-T-GANG到達地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會剝奪全人類的力比多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是這樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最初感受到他們的存在的時候 就有一種很可怕的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了迫不得已的時候我們還有哲平在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次如果再變成KILL-T-GANG的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我不確定能否保持自我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 還是不要小看他們比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星齒輪裝置是因為想要無限的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才讓小華開動Livlaster的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他們沒有人能開動Livlaster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.71,0:07:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一邊吃西瓜一邊聊這種事 不覺得很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 還有哈密瓜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈密瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈密瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是哈密瓜要放到明天吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失望…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失望…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們4人再一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈密瓜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有將種子留給你哦 皮兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 皮兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KILL-T-GANG會行動？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說馬上就會行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:07:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…松鼠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒有檢測到任何AEO或NEO的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說大體上知道他們所使用生命力能量的時間和地點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要申請對這個地區進行核打擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在還不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 今晚肯定會行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏大地在Earthengine的駕駛艙裡待機了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine已經修好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麼 大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經在模擬戰中學會了基本操作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學部長！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓練Earth Drive是總部的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有很好的資質
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨時抱佛腳的訓練能起到什麼作用！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差點死了兩次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你一點都不害怕嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我真的非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我只是個普通的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果不打倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就沒有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而希望只有做出決斷才能孕育出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射程序 就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是愚民們的光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得Albion會為了這幫傢伙而背叛我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你能想像自己不再擁有長生不老之身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:10:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 這是最棒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到AEO…是KILL-T-GANG！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.69,0:10:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現地點位於第一防禦圈的γ區域內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種預測能力是你的奇異能力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是皮兹告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮兹是不會說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能預知生命力能量發動的能力！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬火箭 發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認Earthengine的能量填充
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine從天馬火箭分離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine Expand！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初出現的那隻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine與KILL-T-GANG接觸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊都沒有命中！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只要打中就可以擊落它的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Abreaction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有什麼東西會過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地有危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平跟我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 哲平…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大地一把！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次如果再變成那副身體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有自信會繼續保持現在的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢Forte！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拖拖拉拉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天還要一起吃哈密瓜的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要4人湊到一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須是我們4人才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.82,0:13:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我們4人再一起來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地就拜託給你了 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AMAROK嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了另一台KILL-T-GANG！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Type-1！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:27.55,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}無限に響く声は優しい記憶のしらべ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:27.55,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}無盡迴響的聲音 是那些美麗記憶奏起的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:37.47,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}いつか交わしたはずの約束の光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:37.47,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}是過去我們所許下的約定的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:15:00.74,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}心の片隅で孤独をなぞる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:15:00.74,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}在心中的一隅映出來的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近戰對你不利 盡可能的拉開距離 大地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:10.29,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}どこかで待つ日々を思い出すように
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:10.29,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}仿佛要勾起我在那處等待的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:19.84,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}ほころぶつぼみに　未来を映して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:19.84,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}綻放的花蕾 映出了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:30.23,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}さよならをくれる君を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:30.23,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}我要去尋找當日告別的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:39.67,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}無限に咲く思いは空に浮かぶ陽だまり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:39.67,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}無盡盛開的思緒 是在空中浮沉的溫暖光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Albion 你打算背叛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:49.69,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}いつか守るべき日の面影の光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:49.69,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}是曾經想要守護的日子的模糊影子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要吞噬所有的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓沒睡醒的Albion清醒過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:07.86,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}無くしたものなんてなかったのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:07.86,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你說從來沒有失去過任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先從你開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:18.08,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}さよならの先で　きっと出会える
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:18.08,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}告別 定是下一次重逢的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同我一起貫穿吧 MALKIN！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們的自主模塊不被破壞 就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:27.74,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}無限に響く声は優しい記憶のしらべ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:27.74,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}無盡迴響的聲音 是那些美麗記憶奏起的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣的 因為你是Albion嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個地球人會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:37.07,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}いつか交わしたはずの約束の光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:37.07,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}過去我們所許下的約定的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你躲不躲我都會射 Albion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是嵐哲平！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:46.51,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}ひらりひらり頬を撫でる柔らかな木漏れ日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:46.51,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}一閃一閃的陽光 透過樹縫輕柔地撫上我的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哲平！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:56.85,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}いつか君に渡すための花束にして
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:56.85,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}我要收集起來 作為日後贈予你的花束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他將自主模塊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將自主模塊自爆嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平自己將自主模塊破壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那一踢將雙腳的微動推進器毀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒他 光憑這點氣勢還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓Albion發狂的嗎 Neoteny？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:17:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該懂得用法吧 大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有這招嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Albion破壞了自己的自主模塊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚真是沉重的一夜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Machine Goodfellow也壞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平他沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脈搏 體溫 腦波和血壓都很正常…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就普通人來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平 你手裡拿著的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Livlaster？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第三把了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撤掉了燈里作為沉睡者的申請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是尊重她本人的意願嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是一部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也並非僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多年來 你就是一言既出堅如磐石的頑固性格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里的性格真的是從你身上一個摸子打出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的性格可沒她那麼壞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像看到了希望呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣想？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看一眼就會懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你是我的前夫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經將情況上報到總部的最高委員會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經同意將其作為最高級機密來處理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得到讓華留在這個基地的批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部和你妻子都非常信賴你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:20:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 你覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打敗了AMAROK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地果然很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是被你嚇到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏大地！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嵐哲平！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢塔華！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜祭燈里！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:22:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們四人從現在起就是這Globe種子島基地獨立游擊部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲夏騎士團的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(580,660)}Midsummer's Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎士團？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真夏」的騎士團…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏大地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式任命你為Earthengline的Driver！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.46,0:22:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這支隊伍的隊長就是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 你就是地球隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長要做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先從吃哈密瓜做起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:42.93,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(914,316)}誕生 仲夏騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ふわり風は彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}清風徐徐吹向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:54.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}涙も連れて行ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:54.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}請把我的眼淚也一起帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}星ほどの思い出たちだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使是那些堪比繁星的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}いいことばっかじゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也不全是快樂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}瞬いて　君と出逢えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那個閃爍的瞬間 我與你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:20.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ねぇ　こんなに近くで遠い今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:20.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今天 這個近在咫尺又如此遙遠的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:31.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}始まる合図はぽつりわたしを呼ぶ声聞こえてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:31.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我聽到了那個開始的信號 在輕輕地呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:40.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}愛してるよりもっと形のない言葉探して行くね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:40.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要尋找比「我愛你」更加飄渺的情話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}すぐ側に歩き出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我從你身邊走出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:50.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}さよならよりもそっと涙が紡いだ恋は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:50.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}比「再見」更會在不經意間催人淚下的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:54.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明日も右ポケットに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:54.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明天依然緊攥在右邊口袋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界は声に溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:57.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}世界充滿著美妙的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:03.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}やっと見つけたんだ　君のとなりを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:03.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我終於找到了與你並肩的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行星齒輪裝置戰鬥的仲夏騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小華的預知能力將我們送到了台場的賭場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.65,0:24:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡 AMAROK和MALKIN出現在了我們的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 新的行星齒輪裝置的成員覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 Captain Earth 第8話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.69,0:24:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作印甦醒之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.72,0:24:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earthengine Scramble！

